title: AlphaTALKS Wall Street Breakfast, June 12: What Moved Markets This Week
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: Stocks had quiet start to the week, with investors anxiously awaiting Thursday's consumer price index report. That exceeded expectations, but apparently not by enough to spook markets. Tech stocks in particular rallied and the S&P 500 closed at a record high on Thursday, June 10. Learn more about your ad choices. Visit megaphone.fm/adchoices
